### Test basic connectivity
GET http://localhost:8081/api/init/check-users

### Initialize notification system
POST http://localhost:8081/api/init/notification-system
Content-Type: application/json

### Fix notification issues (email addresses, settings)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/init/fix-notifications
Content-Type: application/json

### Check notification system status
GET http://localhost:8081/api/notifications/system-status

### Test notification configuration
POST http://localhost:8081/api/notifications/test
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "phone": "+1234567890"
}

### Get all notifications
GET http://localhost:8081/api/notifications

### Trigger automatic notifications manually
POST http://localhost:8081/api/notifications/trigger-automatic